prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor illustration for a greeting card front. A humorous and lighthearted scene featuring cartoon-style versions of a young East Asian man and a young East Asian woman, based on the reference photo. The woman, who is in the foreground, has long dark hair, wears thin gold-rimmed glasses, and is smiling happily. She is wearing a light blue sweatshirt (with no text or logos) and black pants. The man stands behind her, hugging her from the back. He has short, dark, slightly messy hair and a big, joyful smile. He is wearing a tan-colored hoodie and dark maroon pants. The characters are illustrated to highly resemble the people in the photo, maintaining their exact facial features, hairstyles, clothing, and pose. They are standing on a pier, and the background is a soft, impressionistic watercolor wash of a calm bay with a distant shoreline and a cloudy sky, rendered with soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds on a textured paper background.

Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Lao Lao, you're the best... no contest!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
